cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.GR, cs.LG. 

The paper investigates the role of human priors in solving video games, which involves both computer vision and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.AI and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves human-computer interaction, which falls under cs.HC. The paper also manipulates the game environment, which could fall under cs.GR (graphics) or cs.LG (machine learning).
